snippet.title: The Expanse: A Telltale Series - Episode 4: Lady Paramount Trailer
snippet.description:
Drummer has been stranded, left behind by the crew of The Artemis in yet another mutiny. Now, she must hatch a desperate plan to escape the mysterious station where she’s been marooned. Drummer must explore and scavenge what she can to survive, but who will come to her aid now? Belters always find a way.

Episode 4 of The Expanse: A Telltale Series is OUT NOW!
